        <h1>From Pasture to Pajamas: The Complete Manufacturer's Guide to Merino Wool for Baby Sleeping Bags and Sleepsuits</h1>
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span>Published: May 17, 2026</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>By Lianchuang Textile</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

